messages.message:
Hi Brian,

Are you open to connecting? 

Best,
Angela

Hi Brian,

I am looking for a wizard for a fulltime role with 2 of my clients. Are you open to looking at other opportunities?
Best,
Angela 623.505.1260.
Can you find someone to pay me to work on my own ideas? I'm tired of giving up my life for some CEO to hash out their ideas at my expense.

That is the conundrum isn't it? So I am looking for a client in Scottsdale-you talked to my co-worker about it with ICE. Great place to work lots of extra perks-fitness facility, Health clinic, cafeteria, new location off the freeway. And a start up. Are you happy where you are or interested in pursuing other opp.s?
Angela
I already applied at ICE and they turned me down. I don't think they hire people like me.
Any interest in a start up?
I've been working for startups for 8 years. ICE is not a startup. They are a middle man.
I have moved on from ICE- I have another opportunity that is with a startup.
What is the goal of the company?
